The paper deals with face recognition, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of SIFT features and matching techniques also suggests a focus on multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The application of decision theory for fusion of matching scores indicates a possible interest in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
